r size=1> WARNING:  If you want to keep the mystery of all this alive, please read no further.  If you've come hunting for a bit of info, this is the right place.<br>
<br>
Found this linked from the Palo.net boards.  Originally posted on the &quot;Class Guides and FAQs (TL Only)&quot; board by Salaris Lightblade (as team leader I presume).  He apparently leads the raids on Guin, Gaheris and Pend, and was the first to lead a successful Sidi raid to kill Apoc.  Tons of good info here and should be a good reference.<br>
